title: E288 The WWE Interview: Nikki Bella, Bobby Lashley & Riddle

description:
In today’s episode, the boys are joined by WWE Superstars Nikki Bella, Bobby Lashley, & Riddle! They discuss Nikki’s love/hate relationship with her twin sister, popping out a baby on her hit reality TV show (Total Bellas), hidden secrets to become a WWE superstar, Bobby Lashley Vs Logan Paul boxing match, top moments in their careers, diet of a WWE champion, historic rise of RKBro & more…
